<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
</head>
<style>
.titles{
  padding: 40px 40px 0 40px;
}  
.kit{
  width: 300px;
  height: 300px;
}
.line{
  border-style:solid;
  border-width: 1px;
  border-left-width: 0;
  border-right-width: 0;
  border-bottom-width: 0;
  margin: 0 auto 28px ;
}
.kit{
  margin: 7px;
}
.kit:hover{
  transform: translateY(30px);
  /* transform: scale(1.3); */
  box-shadow: 0 8px 16px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
}
.food_container h3{
  text-align: center;
  padding: 23px;
}
.snack{
text-align: center;
}
.snack_menu{
  display: inline-block;
  text-align: center;
}
.snack_menu li{
  list-style: none;
  font-size: 24px;
}

</style>

<body>
  <div class="food_container">
    <h1 class="titles">간편요리</h1>
    <div class="line"></div>
    <div class="easy_food">
      <img class="kit" src="/static/img/hot.png" alt="">
      <img class="kit"src="/static/img/대구.png" alt="">
      <img class="kit"src="/static/img/떡.png" alt="">
      <img class="kit"src="/static/img/크림.png" alt="">
    </div>
    <h3> 캠핑은 언제나 배고프다!</h3>
  </div>
  
  <div class="snack">
    <h1 class="titles">매점</h1>
    <div class="line"></div>
    <ul class="snack_menu">
      <li>숟가락</li>
      <li>젓가락</li>
      <li>포크</li>
      <li>접시</li>
      <li>종이컵</li>
    </ul>
    <ul class="snack_menu">
      <li>부탄가스</li>
      <li>이소가스</li>
      <li>장작</li>
    </ul>
    <ul class="snack_menu">
      <li>라면</li>
      <li>과자</li>
      <li>쌈장</li>
      <li>햇반</li>
    </ul>
    <ul class="snack_menu">
      <li>물</li>
      <li>커피</li>
      <li>술</li>
      <li>탄산음료</li>
      <li>얼음</li>
    </ul>
  </div>




</body>
</html>